                <h1>Effective SBAR Communication in Healthcare</h1>
                <p>SBAR, which stands for Situation, Background, Assessment, and Recommendation, is a communication framework widely used in healthcare settings. It promotes effective information exchange between healthcare professionals, ensuring clarity and conciseness. By using SBAR, teams can improve patient safety and facilitate timely decision-making.</p>
